storyInfo: After their everyday regular training, Dur-nar takes on Reserve Op Team A1 in a combat drill. Experience is the mother of wisdom, and she is ready to make everyone sweat.

attributes.content: That wraps up your regular training for the day!
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You know, when you guys first got here, you'd be dead on the ground after just an hour or so.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Look at you now. None of you are even winded.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Just goes to show that the training did its job.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Beagle, the instructor hasn't finished yet! How could you—
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: It's fine, Fang. I'm not Dobermann. No need to follow the rules to a tee.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Everyone's exhausted after all that training. Let's take it easy. Okay?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You know, you're starting to sound more and more like Dobermann.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Look at you. If you stand up straight, put your hands on your hips, and stare straight into my eyes, it's like you're the spitting image of Dobermann.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: And the way you talk... I guess I needn't say anymore.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: She's right. You're exactly like her~
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: It's not like back when I was in the army. Rhodes Island has a decent team of instructors who provide all reserve operators adequate training, and each of them has their specialty.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Anything that I miss, they'll notice and give you guys a lesson on that, and vice versa.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: That way, rather than leaving our reserve operators' lessons to the whim of some random person, you all receive fairly comprehensive training.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Grace, Fallon, Dobermann, and all the rest.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You can always count on them to teach you what you need to know, and have your back in a fight.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Do your best to learn everything you can from Dobermann, okay? We wouldn't mind having a TA.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Of course, Instructor. Thank you, Instructor!
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: Also, remind me to find the groundskeeper to fix this place up after we're done training.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I forgot to do it before, and Dobermann tore me a new one each and every time. *Sigh*...
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Okay, Fang? Be sure to remind me.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: As you know, that wraps up our regular training for the day.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Though we still have some time left.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: And with it, I want to have a little combat drill with everyone!
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Some of us here haven't been in a drill before, so I'll briefly explain what we'll be doing.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: It may sound kind of fancy, but all we are doing is simulated combat. I will evaluate your combat styles and tell you how you could improve.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (Whispers) Quiet down. Wait till the instructor is done.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Oh, of course, this is going to be a little different than your usual fights.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Mmmhm... you're all here. Let's make this a one-on-five.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I wanted to see the results of your training and check how well all of you could work with each other anyway.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Okay, let's take a break first. Relax, eat some candy or whatever. I'll get some preparations done.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You should relax~ It's not Dobermann we're up against.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Instructor Dur-nar isn't that usually scary, b-but... it's a different story if we're going to be fighting her!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: You know how Instructor Dur-nar does drills with the Guard, Defender, and Vanguard operators, Lava?
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Do you know what she does during those matches?
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Last time, she set her shield down and bludgeoned me with two swords for a whole hour!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: And she was as fast as the wind!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: I used to think of her as a really friendly person. She doesn't yell at us that much, and she treats us to some really tasty food.
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: It wasn't until I fought her for the first time that I found out... Once she starts walloping you, Instructor Dur-nar can be much worse than Instructor Dobermann. I could barely hold my lance up.
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: And you've seen her shield arm, right? When she drops the shield and picks up a sword, she can really strike like lightning.
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: Oh, yeah, I think I know what you mean now. It's just like that time when I was in a shooting match against Meteor at the training grounds, right?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Hehe, she landed five training shots on me in just one minute.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Anyway, if you don't want the living daylights beat out of you, be sure to never, ever underestimate Instructor Dur-nar.
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: She's a seasoned vet, and she'd still be in active service if she wasn't disillusioned with the Columbian army.
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: If she brings another sword, we're as good as dead—
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: Hey, Hibiscus? Did anyone go to Medical today to get some ointment or something for flesh wounds?
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: We get a lot of visitors to the Medical Department every day. I guess you could say scratches and bruises are a dime a dozen there?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Hibiscus, this is important. Work with me here.
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: I was redressing a patient's wound at the ward today. I wasn't in the clinic.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: But I heard this from Sussurro.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Apparently everyone from A4 paid us a visit to get their wounds treated after their training this morning.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Yeah, and it was Instructor Dur-nar who brought them there.
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Does that have something to do with this?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I can't believe not even Melantha and Cardigan could stop her...
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: She might make short work of you guys one on one, but there's five of us.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: There's five of them in A4 too...
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: W-What about it? We're much stronger than A4.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: We can do it! We can...
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: It sounds like you guys aren't that confident. Is she really that scary?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Yeah, looks like you're all ready. Excellent.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Instructor, may I ask a question?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Why did you bring an extra practice sword?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Come on, isn't it obvious? It's for our training, of course.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Man, during the break, I suddenly remembered a combat technique I used back in the day. I really want to try it out on someone.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Oh, of course, I'll be using the same stuff as all of you. Regular training equipment, not those electric swords I modified.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You'd better take it serious. Just because I'm not usually that hard on you guys doesn't mean I'll go easy when we're doing this for real.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: If you don't want me to wipe the floor with you, then face me.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Have you read up on the steps to intercepting the enemy? It's in your training handbook.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: When we start off, we'll be facing each other, but we'll use the whole field after that.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: What are you spacing out for? Shouldn't you be more alert with an enemy right in front of you?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Since this is our first battle, I'll let you girls attack first.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Make sure to work with each other. If you aren't careful, it's going to be no different from me taking all of you on one by one.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Beagle, keep an eye on her...
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: Don't have to tell me twice!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hibiscus, I'm counting on you to heal us up. Beagle has more pressure, so prioritize her.
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: Everyone, keep your eyes on her! As long as we got eyes on her, she doesn't stand a chance!
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: I have a clear shot on her!
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Stand up, all of you. I'll go over where you went wrong.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Lava, we actually had a shot...
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: But how was I supposed to know Beagle would be in the way?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Sounds like we found our problem.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: It's true that there's not much height difference in the terrain here, and those in the back could easily injure your teammates.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Aside from that, Lava, your Originium Arts are not very suitable for a closed environment like this.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: In a situation like this, you could've cast your Arts behind me to limit my movement.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Your teammates were already taking me on face to face.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: So why focus your Arts on me?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You still haven't solved that problem we talked about.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Cardigan really likes to rock around when she's on defense. It may create more openings, but that trick is never going to work on her.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I know you fight like that because you want to play it safe, but when you can't play it safe enough to fend off disruptions, you need to use your techniques to make up for it.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Do you remember what I did just now?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You blocked my attack and slammed my shield, and that led me into the path of Lava's Arts.
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: If Fang had been faster, she could've pushed me back before I rammed into you.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Just like what Kroos did the first time.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: If you want to take my blow by yourself, however, there are three ways you can go about it.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: One, come up with a way to counter the attack and dodge it.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: This will expose your teammates to the enemy for a moment, but if you manage to take the chance and strike, you can quickly return to your defensive position.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Two, bear the impact with your shield.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Your shield is a weapon too. Right when you are about to be rammed, you can use your shield to attack.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Though you must also keep your eyes on your opponent. Don't stagger forward. You'd be giving the enemy a chance to attack your teammates or yourself when you have your back open.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You know why I knocked you back into the path of Lava's Arts? Because you were basically begging me to do it, with your stance and your balance.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: If your defense stance was like this instead...
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You still stepped back, but that doesn't affect Lava or Kroos's attack path in any way.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Good. You should get this down.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You're the team captain. Your job is to command everyone else.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Tell me. How do you confirm your teammate's situations?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You look back to check on your friends. Do you think your enemies will just let this chance slip by?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Did you guys base your positions on your basic coursework's textbook?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: We don't follow it strictly, though.
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: The battlefield is a place of chaos. Doing everything by the book is how mistakes happen.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You need to take on some of Fang's responsibilities. Is that okay?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: But what exactly should I do?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Fang needs eyes in the back of her head, and that's where you come in.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: If you, Lava, and Kroos change your positioning, you need to tell Fang.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: If anything in the environment around you changes, you need to tell her immediately, especially if it happens behind her.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: And if Fang is incapacitated, it falls on you to lead the team.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I shouldn't have shot at Hibiscus.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: I'm not too familiar with what exactly ranged operators do, so I'm not going to say much.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: If we just look at how well you work with your teammates, you're doing pretty well.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Mind telling me how you're doing in the shooting practice matches just so I get a rough idea?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Meteor is usually my teacher there. She always takes me down in no time~
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: It's only been a few minutes.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: We'll be using the training grounds' obstacles next.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: This is a battlefield, and your enemies on the battlefield won't go easy on you.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I hope all of you, maybe I, will get to live for a few seconds longer.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Let's all do our best, girls.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Well, looks like I still have it in me. Awesome.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Yep, and right on time. That concludes our training for today.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Alright, how about I treat all of you to something tasty?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I got some lap cheong imported straight from Yan, marinated in the finest sauces. It's got to be the sweetest and most fragrant thing ever.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: But before that, I need to take you to Medical.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: So that we can both learn where your limits lie.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: So Cardigan and the gang didn't get sent to Medical because of you. I was so scared...
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: I'm not sure about anyone else, but I've got my ways to deal with you girls. I wasn't a soldier all those years for nothing.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I had it figured out a long time ago what exactly to prioritize.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Know that a lot of actual blood and sweat, even the lives of some of my friends, went into these techniques I'm teaching you.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: If I find out you don't have this etched into your brains, I'll bring my electric blade the next time I spar.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Okay, let's get going, then. We'll get a bite to eat once you're done with your checkups.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (What did she want me to do again?)
attributes.name: Fang

attributes.content: Fang, you like spicy, sour stuff?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You see, I got these snacks—
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Perfect timing. You manage the training grounds here, right?
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Y-Yes, Instructor Dobermann. What's the matter?
attributes.name: Logistics Operator

attributes.content: Looks like Dur-nar and her team wrecked some of the equipment and obstacles while they were using this place. My guess is they had a pretty intense sparring match.
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Help me fix it up. I'll be training with some reserve operators later tonight.
attributes.name: Dobermann
